1. **`src/lib/claude-settings.ts`** -- No dependencies on other new files. Can be implemented and tested in isolation.
2. **`src/commands/enable.ts`** and **`src/commands/disable.ts`** -- Depend on `claude-settings.ts` and existing `credentials.ts`.
